{"tid":1463901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"膽粗粗既分享 歡迎比意見","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:04.000Z","uid":299017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4320a0df81fbb7ee048e1b8ed60672daf8a2f1","tid":1463901,"uid":299017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"一直都好想將反送中既起源到而家<br />\n用一啲易上口易記既標語寫出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實作左好幾句<br />\n拖到今日先有勇氣po上網<br />\n其實寫完個陣覺得自己好on9<br />\n唔知寫黎做乜又唔敢見天<br />\n但膽粗粗想試下分享一次<br />\n<br />\n如果反應唔錯 <br />\n想試下文宣宣揚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都會分享更多膠句<br />\n<br />\n真心歡迎大家比意見<br />\n<br />\n多謝抽空睇左既大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖源為:HK01新聞圖片<br />\n<br />\n字源為:本人膠作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4cvF8R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4cvF8R.png&h=8fae957f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}